How to use the Coles catalogue online

  • Click on any item on the page for more information
  • Click the arrow on the right to turn to the next page, or the left arrow to go back a page
  • Add something to your cart by selecting it, modifying the quantity and clicking 'add'
  • View your cart in the top right corner
  • Change the catalogue view by selecting one of the options on the top left above the catalogue
  • Share it with a friend by clicking 'email' just above the catalogue
  • Find a specific product by typing into the search box
